Package oogasalad.editor.model.data

Class EditorLevelData

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.editor.model.data.EditorLevelData
public class EditorLevelData extends Object
Represents the level data used by the editor, including groups, layers, and mappings between editor objects and their respective layers. This class manages collections of editor objects organized by layers and groups. It also loads editor configuration properties from a resource file.
Author:
Jacob You
